discounts.description: You'll receive a 12% guaranteed discount off our electricity usage and supply charges.

electricityContract.variation: We may vary your rates and charges at any time, including if any underlying information is incorrect, you get a new meter or your distributor changes your tariff. We'll give you advance notice of any change, which may be on your bill.

incentives.description: 100% of your electricity will be matched with GreenPower, sourced from accredited, renewable electricity sources.

eligibility.description: To be eligible for this offer you must be a current My NRMA member. Your membership number must be provided at the time of sign up.

greenPowerCharges.description: To participate in the GreenPower accredited program a daily charge of 14.28c (inc GST) will be applied to your electricity bill.
